                    >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2
        class="mx-auto mt-20 text-center mb-8 text-emerald-600 text-transparent bg-clip-text text-3xl border-b-2 border-emerald- font-semibold w-fit"
    >
        Not the right time? <h1></h1>
    </h2>

    <p class="font-semibold mb-20 text-center">
        We'll be here when you are ready!
    </p>
